{
  "title": "Checklist for DMCS on-premise onboarding",
  "slug": "checklist-for-on-premise-production",
  "categorySlug": "it-onboarding",
  "html": "<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell \" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-1 dnd-section kb-article-row-0-padding\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-cell dnd-column\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"cell\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-2 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-2\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-3 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h1 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-3_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">Checklist for DMCS on-premise onboarding</h1>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-4 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <h2 id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-4_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_text_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_text_field\">This checklist is for pre-production of DMCS on-premise or in AWS/Azure</h2>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid-wrapper row-depth-1 row-number-5 dnd-row\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid \">\n<div class=\"span12 widget-span widget-type-custom_widget dnd-module\" style=\"\" data-widget-type=\"custom_widget\" data-x=\"0\" data-w=\"12\">\n<div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_module\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"module\">\n  <div id=\"hs_cos_wrapper_kb-article-module-5_\" class=\"hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_inline_richtext_field\" style=\"\" data-hs-cos-general-type=\"widget\" data-hs-cos-type=\"inline_richtext_field\"><ul>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Ubuntu 24.04 has been installed on the target server (DMCS)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">The DMCS has a minimum of <strong>128 GB RAM, 16 threads, 1 TB disk, and no less than 15% of the source data</strong></li>\n<li>The root partition on the D&amp;MC Server has a minimum of 60 GB of free space</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A 1 TB backup disk has been mounted on /mnt/data/</li>\n<li>The domain compliant.your company.local or compliant.yourcompany.com has been added to the company DNS, and the URL is pointing to the DMCS</li>\n<li>Domain and pfx certificate + password has been send <a href=\"mailto:support@dataandmore.com\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-weight: 400;\">support@dataandmore.com</a></li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">DMZ is properly configured and the proper ports are open/closed</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">You have received VPN configuration file from D&amp;M and VPN is running</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">The VPN is up and connected to clientvpn.gdpr.dataandmore.com</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A&nbsp; username and password&nbsp; with sudo rights for the D&amp;MC Server have been given to D&amp;M</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Any file shares that should be scanned are mounted on the D&amp;MC Server under the path /mnt/data/fileshare/ and added to the fstab</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">All cloud data have been registered and handed over to D&amp;M</li>\n<li>The reg edit PowerShell has been run on the participants in PC (optional)</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">AD groups have been set up for user segmentation, and group IDs have been handed over to D&amp;M</li>\n<li>The end-user laptop has HTTPS access to the DMCS</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">End users are accessing the servers using Chrome&nbsp;<br><br></li>\n</ul></div>\n</div>\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div><!--end row-->\n</div><!--end row-wrapper -->\n\n</div><!--end widget-span -->\n</div>\n</div>",
  "sourceUrl": "https://support.dataandmore.com/en/knowledge/checklist-for-on-premise-production"
}